author: Rebeca Piccardo
title: Man charged in 2011 Coral Springs murder is extradited to Broward
text:
Man charged in 2011 Coral Springs murder is extradited to Broward Jason Martinez Broward Sheriff's Office/Courtesy Jason Martinez, 28, was charged in the 2011 murder of Michael Todd Hamilton, who was found stabbed and with his throat cut inside his apartment. Martinez, a former Coral Springs resident, was extradited Thursday from New York to Broward County.
